    <item>
      <title>Meta 的目标是 105 亿美元，这是其最大的高等级债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/meta-meta-kicks-off-bond-sale-as-companies-storm-high-grade-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在发行价值 105 亿美元的投资级债券，这是其有史以来最大规模的债券发行，这将增加其现金储备，因为该公司正在大力投资人工智能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/meta-meta-kicks-off-bond-sale-as-companies-storm-high-grade-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德资产利润未达预期，资产规模达到约 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/brookfield-asset-management-profits-rise-assets-hit-1-trillion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 表示，其管理的资产增至创纪录的约 1 万亿美元，并报告利润较上年同期有所增加，但仍低于分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/brookfield-asset-management-profits-rise-assets-hit-1-trillion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
